<Class name="HMS_MovementClearanceAgent" id="e541206f-ab42-4190-981c-5ffaa8d58f5c">
    <superclass name="CM_Agent"/>
    <transient/>
    <persistentAllowed/>
    <sharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassPersistentAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>dh - 27/3/2008

This class has been created to begin the refactoring of voyage clearances
in particular to fix fault 15969 and 16146

I have had to interrupt development to carry on with some more urgent work.

If this class is not in use and a lot of time has passed, this class can be 
removed (or preferably completed).</text>
    <DbClassMap file="edi"/>
